Thank you for using Charge-R.

Charge-R is an independent electric vehicle range estimation app designed to provide informational driving range calculations based on user-selected conditions. The app works fully offline and does not collect or transmit any personal data.

Support & Contact

If you have questions, feedback, or encounter any issues while using the app, you can contact us at:

