Privacy

Charge-R does not require account creation.
All data entered by the user is stored locally on the device only and is never shared with third parties.

Disclaimer

Charge-R provides estimated results for informational purposes only. Actual driving range may vary depending on real-world conditions, vehicle condition, and driving behavior.
